<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff4d4d;
            background: #f8d7da;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>You have requested to reset your password. Use the code below to proceed:</p>
        <div class="code"><%= secretCode %></div>
        <p>This code is valid for only a limited time. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Thank you!<br> <strong>Your Company Team</strong></p>
        <p class="footer">If you have any issues, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@yourcompany.com">support@yourcompany.com</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
